title: KGMU Recruitment 2025 - Apply Offline for 09 Senior Resident Posts
description: The King George's Medical University (KGMU) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 09 Senior Resident Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their MD/MS can apply for the KGMU Recruitment 2025 . The interested applicants can apply in offline mode.
